Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:20:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn华文中宋\fs54\bord0\pos(951,654)}“回”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:20:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn华文中宋\fs54\bord0\pos(951,654)}“来”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn华文中宋\fs54\bord0\pos(951,654)}“了”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn华文中宋\fs54\bord0\pos(951,654)}“风”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn华文中宋\fs54\bord0\pos(951,654)}“见”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn华文中宋\fs54\bord0\pos(951,654)}“雄”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn华文中宋\fs54\bord0\pos(951,654)}“二”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn华文中宋\fs60\bord0\pos(942,654)}…我…回来了…风见…雄二…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9029  9029
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战失败了  9029号要怎么处置
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拘捕后进行回收
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用药也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.84,0:22:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.44,0:22:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.41,0:23:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人遗憾  不过这次就要请他走下舞台了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了  由美美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少见你这么慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电视  电视直播的新闻你们没看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直播？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直在看德夫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之快看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莳菜  先换到无线频道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.99,0:23:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击大使馆的恐怖分子是以希斯·奥斯洛为首的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参加袭击的成员中很可能有一个名为风见雄二的日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回  白翼之种Ⅰ
